title: If You Had Invested $25,000 Into Shares of Alphabet in 2019, This Is How Much You Would Have Today
description: Incidentally, if you had invested $25,000 into shares of Alphabet (NASDAQ: GOOG) (NASDAQ: GOOGL) on Jan. 2, 2019, you'd have $43,800 today.  With so much traffic, it's no wonder the company can cash in by selling hyper-targeted ads on its platform that generate massive sales for the company.
